	(text "Rule of thumb\n C_{a}, C_{b} = 2 * C_{L} - 2 * C_{stray}\nTypical stray cap, maybe ~5pF\n\nFor 12pF C_{L} = ( (C_{a} * C_{b})/(C_{a} * C_{b})) + C_{stray}\nuse 14pF"
